      "description": "$48,500 - Beautiful mint-condition classic that has been exceptionally well preserved and cared for. It shows wonderfully inside and out, with a clean, crisp, well-kept feel throughout, and it\u2019s the kind of car that\u2019s ready to impress at a glance and reward close inspection. A standout example for someone looking for a top-tier, honestly represented classic.",
