    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptionally well-kept, mint-condition example that presents exactly the way buyers hope to find one. The paint, trim, and interior all show beautifully with a fresh, clean appearance, and the car gives the impression of careful ownership and consistent upkeep. It looks complete, highly sorted, and ready to be enjoyed immediately, with the kind of overall condition that stands out from ordinary driver-quality cars. Buyers should expect a car that shows extremely well throughout and needs little beyond routine care.",
