      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Solid fair-condition driver that looks complete and usable, but shows its age in both cosmetics and overall presentation. Expect visible wear to the paint, trim, and interior, along with the kind of imperfections and deferred upkeep you\u2019d expect from an older car that has been driven and enjoyed. It should suit someone looking for an honest, presentable car to use and improve over time, rather than a fully sorted or show-quality example.",
